"><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight\">Survey Feedback</h1><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl\">Share your experience with job boards and help us improve the efficiency scoring</p></div></div></div><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">Employer Survey</h2><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 text-gray-300 mb-6\"><p class=\"mb-4\">Your feedback helps us understand job board efficiency from a hiring perspective. This survey takes about 5-10 minutes to complete.</p><div class=\"bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-4 mt-4\"><p class=\"text-sm text-blue-400\"><strong>We value your input:</strong> Your responses directly influence our efficiency scoring algorithm, helping employers and job seekers make better decisions about which boards to use.</p></div></article><form class=\"space-y-6 max-w-2xl\"><fieldset class=\"space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800/50\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Company Information</legend><div><label for=\"companyName\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Company Name *</label><input id=\"companyName\" type=\"text\" name=\"companyName\" placeholder=\"Acme Corp\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"industry\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Industry *</label><input id=\"industry\" type=\"text\" name=\"industry\" placeholder=\"e.g., Technology, Finance, Healthcare\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"companySize\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Company Size *</label><select id=\"companySize\" name=\"companySize\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"startup\">Startup (1-50)</option><option value=\"small\">Small (51-200)</option><option value=\"medium\" selected=\"\">Medium (201-1000)</option><option value=\"large\">Large (1001-5000)</option><option value=\"enterprise\">Enterprise (5000+)</option></select></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800/50\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Hiring Metrics</legend><div><label for=\"hireCount\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Successful Hires from Board (Last 30 Days) *</label><input id=\"hireCount\" type=\"number\" name=\"hireCount\" placeholder=\"e.g., 5\" min=\"0\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">Number of candidates successfully hired</p></div><div><label for=\"timeToHire\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Average Time to Hire (Days) *</label><input id=\"timeToHire\" type=\"number\" name=\"timeToHire\" placeholder=\"e.g., 14\" min=\"0\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">From job posting to successful hire</p></div><div><label for=\"hireCost\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Average Cost per Hire ($) *</label><input id=\"hireCost\" type=\"number\" name=\"hireCost\" placeholder=\"e.g., 2500\" min=\"0\" step=\"0.01\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">Total cost including recruitment fees and time</p></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800/50\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Quality Assessment</legend><div><label for=\"postingQuality\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Quality of Candidate Responses *</label><select id=\"postingQuality\" name=\"postingQuality\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"poor\">Poor - Few qualified candidates</option><option value=\"fair\">Fair - Some qualified candidates</option><option value=\"good\" selected=\"\">Good - Most candidates qualified</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - High-quality candidates</option><option value=\"exceptional\">Exceptional - Exceptional quality</option></select><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">Rating of applicant quality from this board</p></div><div><label for=\"responseQuality\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">Board Posting Experience *</label><select id=\"responseQuality\" name=\"responseQuality\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"poor\">Poor - Difficult to use</option><option value=\"fair\">Fair - Some issues</option><option value=\"good\" selected=\"\">Good - Overall satisfactory</option><option value=\"excellent\">Excellent - Easy to use</option><option value=\"exceptional\">Exceptional - Best experience</option></select><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">Your experience posting and managing listings</p></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-4 p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg bg-gray-800/50\"><legend class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4\">Additional Feedback</legend><div><label for=\"generalNotes\" class=\"block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide\">General Notes</label><textarea id=\"generalNotes\" name=\"generalNotes\" placeholder=\"Any additional comments about your experience with this job board...\" rows=\"4\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all resize-none\"></textarea><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1.5\">Optional: Share any additional insights</p></div></fieldset><div class=\"flex gap-3 pt-4\"><button class=\"font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-gray-900 active:scale-95 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-blue-500 text-white shadow-md hover:shadow-lg px-6 py-3 sm:py-3.5 text-base sm:text-lg  disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\" type=\"submit\">✓ Submit Survey</button><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 self-center\">* Required fields</p></div></form></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">About This Survey</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2\">📋 What We Ask</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Company info, hiring metrics (time to hire, cost), candidate quality assessment, and positioning experience feedback.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2\">🔒 Your Data</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">All responses are anonymized. We never share individual company data publicly, only aggregate insights.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2\">💡 How It Helps</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Your feedback improves our scoring algorithm, making the platform more accurate for everyone.</p></article></div></section><section class=\"mb-8 \"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Why do you need this information?</h4><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Employer feedback is crucial for real-world validation of our efficiency scoring. We want to ensure the algorithm reflects actual hiring outcomes.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Is my company information public?</h4><p class=\"text-gray-400\">No. We only use aggregate data in reports. Individual company responses remain confidential.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Can I submit multiple surveys?</h4><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Yes! We encourage you to submit feedback for each job board you use. This helps us build a comprehensive picture.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-2\">How often should I submit surveys?</h4><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Submit when you have completed a hiring cycle (successfully hired someone) from a board, or at minimum monthly to track trends.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors duration-200 \"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-2\">What happens with the data?</h4><p class=\"text-gray-400\">Data is used to improve our efficiency scores, identify trends in hiring success, and provide insights to job board operators.</p></article></div></section></main></div></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/dashboard/surveys\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"6lHlMA4-wlOe2P63cYf-h\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}